# Security Base Boundaries

## Approved sources

- Write code using this repository and approved internal libraries only
- Do not paste or adapt code from external websites or unknown repositories

## Package policy

- Import only packages listed in the app repo `scripts/approved-packages.txt`
- Do not run `pip install` for unapproved packages

## Sensitive operations

- Do not modify CI/CD deploy pipelines unless explicitly asked by platform engineering
- Do not commit secrets, tokens, or credentials

## When unsure

- Ask the engineer before adding a dependency or integrating an external service
